high_descs: Move to stand at the closest edge of the coffee table.
Pick up the blue pencil that is closest to you and closest to the fingers of the hand sculpture.
Turn and move to stand in front of the lamp in the pink lamp in the corner.
Turn the lamp on while holding the pencil.
anns.task_desc: Turn the lamp on  in the corner.

high_descs: Go to the table in front of you.
Pick up the pen nearest to you on the table.
Turn around and go to the lamp to the left.
anns.task_desc: View a pen by lamp light.

high_descs: Pick up the blue pen on the table.
Walk across the room to the lamp in the corner by the pair of boots.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a blue pen by the light of the lamp.
